### Package Overview

| Package | Files | Purpose |
|---------|-------|---------|
| `main` | App.java | Application entry point, menu system |
| `model` | Expense.java, Category.java | Data models (POJOs) |
| `database` | DatabaseConnection.java, ExpenseDAO.java | Database connectivity & CRUD |
| `service` | ExpenseService.java, ReportService.java, ValidationService.java | Business logic & validation |
| `utils` | CSVExporter.java, DateUtils.java, ConsoleUtils.java | Utility functions |
| `exception` | DatabaseException.java, ValidationException.java | Custom exceptions |

