## ğŸ”Œ API Reference

### ExpenseService

```java
// Create expense
boolean createExpense(String desc, double amt, LocalDate date, 
                      String cat, String method, String notes)

// Retrieve
List<Expense> getAllExpenses()
Expense getExpenseById(int id)
List<Expense> filterByCategory(String category)
List<Expense> filterByDateRange(LocalDate from, LocalDate to)
List<Expense> filterByMonth(int month, int year)

// Sort
List<Expense> sortByDateDescending()
List<Expense> sortByAmountDescending()

// Update/Delete
boolean updateExpense(Expense expense)
boolean deleteExpense(int id)
```

### ReportService

```java
// Reports
Map<String, Object> getMonthlySummary(int month, int year)
Map<String, Double> getCategoryWiseReport()
Map<String, String> getCategoryBudgetStatus()
double getTotalExpenses()
double getYearToDateTotal(int year)

// Display
void printMonthlySummary(int month, int year)
void printCategoryReport()
```

### ValidationService

```java
// Validation
boolean validateExpenseData(String desc, double amt, 
                           LocalDate date, String cat)
List<String> getValidCategories()
List<String> getValidPaymentMethods()
```

